</div><div class="lyt-image">
<a class="boxer" target="_blank" href="https://img.furusato-tax.jp/img/x/gcf/project/progresses/20210729/2_135e51ec4291b74d5eab941c8d4ddfb59eac68af.jpg"><img alt decoding="async" src="https://img.furusato-tax.jp/img/x/gcf/project/progresses/20210729/2_135e51ec4291b74d5eab941c8d4ddfb59eac68af.jpg" /></a>
